Comment: The calculations are provided for the energy range from
Rutherford scattering up to 3.5 MeV. The results reported in
Phys. Rev. 112 (1958) 1702 are reproduced in the calculations.
More recent measurements performed in the energy range of 1.5 -
2.7 MeV (see NIM B83 (1988) 628) are in a good agreement with
calculations except for normalization, which is overestimated by
about 5 per cent. 

